# Stray output dirs from running tooling with the repo as cwd
# - visorplus assess writes to ./<IP-with-dots-as-underscores>/ when -out
#   is omitted or relative; the IP-shaped dirname catches that.
# - jaxen / goharvester writes empire.db to cwd when invoked there.
/[0-9]*_[0-9]*_[0-9]*_[0-9]*/
/empire.db
/visorplus-output/

